Sync
public static class Sync.Status
extends Sync.History
implements Sync.StatusColumns

Provides constants and utility methods to access and use the authority history table, which contains information about syncs aggregated by account and authority. All the HistoryColumns except for EVENT are present, plus the AuthorityHistoryColumns.
